{
  "id": "RAW_987412ff",
  "title": "刚刚，DeepSeek 开源「记忆」模块 Engram，梁文锋署名论文同步发布",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5ODkzMzMwMQ==&mid=2650450732&idx=1&sn=5f9b1f2b3ceb3bd37e5ca808b30cfb0e",
  "date": "2026-01-13 02:17:00",
  "author": "AINLP",
  "siteName": "AINLP",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"background-color:inherit;font-size:17px;\">就在十几小时前，DeepSeek 团队开源了</span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-layout-id&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;font-size: 17px;font-weight: 300;color: rgba(0,0,0,0.9);margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 2.0;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\" style=\"background-color:inherit;font-size:17px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">“</span>记忆模块”</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"background-color:inherit;font-size:17px;\">&nbsp;<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Engram</span>：</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"502967075\" data-ratio=\"0.5361111111111111\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7a330144&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FnW2ZPfuYqSJqFRlZG3y4l6FTDXiaUiaWhj21U69oLt7lzSUZPia4E5fvY9e097uKTOJlibheuDjXA0NBI66hqDI32g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"0\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.544px;display:inline !important;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;float:none;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:left;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 128, 255);\">项目地址：<a href=\"https://github.com/deepseek-ai/Engram\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/deepseek-ai/Engram</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"0\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">并同步发布了一篇看起来并不“热闹”，但分量很重的论文：<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">《Conditional Memory via Scalable Lookup: Engram》</span></span><span style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\">，这篇论文与北京大学合作完成，作者中同样有梁文锋署名。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"502967074\" data-ratio=\"0.5325779036827195\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"706\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=101c0a31&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FnW2ZPfuYqSJqFRlZG3y4l6FTDXiaUiaWhjTGsy5sl43wwW0ia2nkABw2beeH5VJ3MbsFyVsFbYYbZj3GcjZDfsPCw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(0, 128, 255);\">论文地址：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(0, 128, 255);\"><a href=\"https://github.com/deepseek-ai/Engram/blob/main/Engram_paper.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/deepseek-ai/Engram/blob/main/Engram_paper.pdf</a></span></span></p>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"2\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">没有新榜单刷屏，也没有参数规模翻倍，但如果你把它放进 DeepSeek 过去一年的技术脉络里看，会发现这是一步<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">非常关键、而且来得很克制的更新</span>：</span></p>\n  <blockquote style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:15px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\">\n   <p data-start=\"679\" data-end=\"703\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><strong data-start=\"679\" data-end=\"703\"><span leaf=\"\">他们开始认真处理“大模型记忆”这件事了。</span></strong></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <h1 data-layout-id=\"5\" style=\"font-size: 20px;font-weight: 400;color: rgba(43, 119, 191, 1);margin-bottom: 12px;line-height: 2.0;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">为什么「记忆」会成为一个需要单独解决的问题？</span></span></h1>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"6\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">在今天的 Transformer 里，所有信息——无论是推理、常识还是实体知识——</span></p>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"7\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">本质上都要通过<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">多层注意力和前馈网络反复计算</span>出来。这在能力规模较小时还能接受，但模型一旦变大，问题就变得越来越明显：</span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p data-layout-id=\"9\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">固定知识（人名、术语、公式）被反复“算”</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p data-layout-id=\"10\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">前几层大量算力被消耗在“重建已知信息”上</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p data-layout-id=\"11\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">真正的推理深度反而被压缩</span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"12\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">换句话说：<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">模型并不是不会记，而是没有“直接查记忆”的能力。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"14\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">DeepSeek 的判断很直接：如果某些信息本质上是静态的、可复用的，那它就不该占用推理预算。</span></p>\n  <h1 data-layout-id=\"17\" style=\"font-size: 20px;font-weight: 400;color: rgba(43, 119, 191, 1);margin-bottom: 12px;line-height: 2.0;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Engram 在做的事：给 Transformer 加一个「查表通道」</span></span></h1>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"18\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Engram 的核心思想并不复杂，但非常“工程化”：</span></p>\n  <blockquote style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:15px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\">\n   <p data-start=\"1073\" data-end=\"1104\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><strong data-start=\"1073\" data-end=\"1104\"><span leaf=\"\">把“记忆”从计算路径中拆出来，变成一条独立的稀疏通道。</span></strong></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"20\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">具体来说，Engram 做了三件关键的事：</span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p data-layout-id=\"21\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">用 N-gram 作为记忆索引</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p data-layout-id=\"22\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">把局部 token 序列当作 key，而不是整段语义</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p data-layout-id=\"23\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">通过哈希表直接查 embedding</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"24\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">查表是 O(1)，不需要多层网络计算，<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">由上下文决定这条记忆是否生效</span>，防止误命中和语义污染，这不是 RAG，也不是外部搜索，而是<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">模型内部的条件记忆机制</span>。</span></p>\n  <h1 data-layout-id=\"29\" style=\"font-size: 20px;font-weight: 400;color: rgba(43, 119, 191, 1);margin-bottom: 12px;line-height: 2.0;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">一个重要变化：稀疏不只属于 MoE 了</span></span></h1>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"30\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">论文里有一个非常值得注意的观点：<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">稀疏并不只意味着“少算一点”，也可以意味着“少记一点”。</span>DeepSeek 把稀疏预算拆成了两部分：</span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p data-layout-id=\"33\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">条件计算（MoE 专家）</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p data-layout-id=\"34\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">条件记忆（Engram 表）</span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"35\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">实验结果显示：当把一部分稀疏参数从 MoE 转移给 Engram 时，模型性能不仅没有下降，反而在多个任务上显著提升。</span></p>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"37\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这背后的逻辑其实很清晰：<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">当模型不再用计算去模拟记忆，计算本身反而变得更有效。</span></span></p>\n  <h1 data-layout-id=\"40\" style=\"font-size: 20px;font-weight: 400;color: rgba(43, 119, 191, 1);margin-bottom: 12px;line-height: 2.0;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">更反直觉的地方：推理能力也在提升</span></span></h1>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"41\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">直觉上，增加“记忆模块”应该主要提升知识类任务。但论文的实验结果却显示：</span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p data-layout-id=\"43\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">推理（BBH、ARC）显著提升</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p data-layout-id=\"44\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">代码与数学能力同步增强</span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"45\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">原因并不神秘。当静态知识在浅层就被“直接取出”，后续层就不必再反复构造语义表示，相当于<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">为推理腾出了更多有效深度</span>。论文中的分析结果显示：Engram 模型在浅层就达到了基线模型更深层的表示水平。</span></p>\n  <h1 data-layout-id=\"50\" style=\"font-size: 20px;font-weight: 400;color: rgba(43, 119, 191, 1);margin-bottom: 12px;line-height: 2.0;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">一个非常现实的工程优势：记忆不一定要放在 GPU 上</span></span></h1>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"51\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Engram 还有一个很容易被低估的系统层优势：<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">它的访问是完全可预测的。</span>因为记忆索引只依赖输入 token，系统可以提前知道接下来要查哪些位置，从而：</span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p data-layout-id=\"54\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">将超大记忆表 offload 到 CPU</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p data-layout-id=\"55\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">通过预取与计算重叠，几乎不影响吞吐</span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"56\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">实验显示，即使记忆规模达到<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">100B 参数量级</span>，推理速度损失仍控制在几个百分点以内。这意味着什么？</span></p>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"58\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">模型容量第一次不再完全受制于 GPU 显存。</span></span></p>\n  <h1 data-layout-id=\"60\" style=\"font-size: 20px;font-weight: 400;color: rgba(43, 119, 191, 1);margin-bottom: 12px;line-height: 2.0;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">写在最后：这一步，可能比参数翻倍更重要</span></span></h1>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"61\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Engram 并不是一个炫技式模块，它更像是 DeepSeek 对一个长期问题的回应：</span></p>\n  <blockquote style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:15px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\">\n   <p data-start=\"2102\" data-end=\"2123\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><strong data-start=\"2102\" data-end=\"2123\"><span leaf=\"\">大模型到底应该用计算，还是用记忆？</span></strong></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"63\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">答案不是二选一，而是<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">各司其职</span>。当静态知识不再挤占推理路径，Transformer 才真正有空间去做它最擅长的事——复杂、组合式的思考。</span></p>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"65\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这一步，也许不会立刻改变排行榜，但它很可能会成为<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">下一代稀疏模型的基础构件之一</span>。</span></p>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"59\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:300;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 0px 24px;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><strong data-start=\"1979\" data-end=\"2074\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">附该论文英中对照版，仅供学习参考，感兴趣的朋友可以关注AINLP公众号回复'engram'获取该技术报告英中对照版pdf全文：</span></span></stro